headline.main: Kyle Busch Wins Atlanta Xfinity Race for 2nd Year in a Row
headline.print_headline: Kyle Busch Wins Atlanta Xfinity Race for 2nd Year in a Row

lead_paragraph: After a bunch of close calls at Atlanta Motor Speedway, Kyle Busch has found the winning touch in the NASCAR Xfinity Series.
